.DT
set_shop_type
Disk World creator help
set_shop_type

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
set_shop_type -  This method sets the type of the shop.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void set_shop_type(string ty)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^ty%^RESET%^ - the type of the shop

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/shops/general_shop.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method sets the type of the shop.  This controls what sort of
mechandise the shop will buy and sell.


The types of allowed shops are: 
.EP
.SO 6 2 -10

	*	jewelery 
	*	armoury 
	*	clothes 
	*	magic 
	*	none set (ie: 0, general type) 
.EO
.SP 5 5

.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
query_shop_type(), set_strict_shop()
.EP

